creator: PT Infoflow Solutions
descriptionHtml:
PX provides you access all HR operations on your phone. It’s an app built with the intention to simplify and help talents administer the so-called annoying HR operations. Whether it’s tracking your on-boarding progress, submitting your leaves or updating your personal information for insurance, PX is there to help you!
What you’ll like:
- Contract signed, remotely
Sign your contract digitally and have it securely saved in your drive for easy access
- Less nervous on the first day**
Easily follow the tasks on PX, so you know what to do as a new kid on the block!
- Track your leave
Make sure you take enough rest this year by keeping track of your leaves on px!
We know you’re excited, but PX is currently only open for internal use of Bank Jago, DKatalis and Amaan Digital Platform. For more information and inquiries, please reach out to: px@dkatalis.com
Release v0.2
We’re thrilled to release pX for the first time to talent! Get busy exploring this new tool and we’ll be ready to take your feedback. It’s an app built to help you, after all!
This release includes a few key features, including preboarding, onboarding, task management, mood meter and leave management. More to come!
descriptionShort: PX provides you access all HR operations on your phone.
